IBM Data Analyst: Plotly Dash Dasboard Exercise

Disclaimer: 
  This project is pedagogical in nature to apply the skills I learned in the IBM Data Analyst course.

Business Task:
  Provide historical Airline metrics for business stakeholders to display average sales breakdowns in and out of recession. Additionally, drill down the same statstics by year.

Goal:
  Create a Dashboard using an IDE with Python and the Plotly package. 

Deliverable:
  Plotly Dashboard
